<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Tune² empowers your tunes.</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=iso-8859-1" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="lib/bootswatch/cyborg/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/welcome.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Tune²</a>
        <div class="nav navbar-nav nav-pills pull-right" id="betalogo">
            Beta
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="splash">
      <div class="container contents mainhome">

          <h1>Let people play their favourite music.</h1>
          <h3>TuneSquared, the social playlist.</h3> <br />
          <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary home-action-btn" href="#" id="create">Create a party</a>
          <a class="btn btn-large btn-default home-action-btn" href="/m">Join a party</a>
           <br />
          <br /> <br /><br /> <br /><br /><br />
      </div>
    </div>



    <div class="container demoline">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="contents col-12">
          <center>
          <h2>Search, add and vote for songs to craft the ultimate soundtrack.</h2>
          <h3>Everyone. Together.</h3>
          <p class="lead">With TuneSquared, everyone can be the DJ. <br />All you need is a phone with internet connection. Easy.</p>


          </center>
        </div>


        <div class="contents col-6">

          <center>
            <h4>How does it work?</h4>
          </center>
          <p class="lead">When a song ends, simply the one with the highest rating in the playlist starts.</p>


          <center>
            <h4>Small music collection?</h4>
          </center>
          <p class="lead">Any song on Youtube can be accessed using the search feature (with more sources to be added soon), no worries.</p>

        </div>

        <div class="contents col-6">
          <center>
            <h4>Planning a party?</h4>
          </center>
          <p class="lead">Don't lose hours looking for music, let your guests make the playlist on the spot. (Honestly, happens anyway, they always want to plug in their phones and show you something.) </p>


          <center>
            <h4>On your own?</h4>
           </center>


          <p class="lead">You can control the music straight from your smartphone from the comfort of your own sofa.</p>

        </div>

        <div class="contents col-12">
          <center>
          <h2>Create your Party now and stay tuned!</h2>
          <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary home-action-btn" href="#" id="create2">Give it a try!</a>

          </center>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
      window.require = {
          waitSeconds: 90
      };
    </script>
    <script data-main="js/welcome" src="lib/require.js"></script>

    <div class="container">
      <% include footer.ejs %>
    </div>

    <div id="create-dialog"></div>

